"replyTime":"2019-01-16T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你呢個體重跑步會對隻<span style=\"color: red;\">腳</span>好大負荷，你可以試下游水，單車等等俾身體更加適應下先先去跑步。<br />\n我媽媽都係咁而減左不少體重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"503d510eef8a39b3a7526c295bdb3bc9e4205708","tid":981314,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"飲食 <br />\n<br />\n你想減得健康 搵營養師"},{"pid":"05c0d0307733a50fbe89c9fe49e76a1b2dd9014e","tid":981314,"uid":171743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9051b6ff751cba26596321eaedf32379e25ad35","tid":981314,"uid":170934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"跑步對肥人膝頭太大負擔，可以去游水，同時間係飲食入手<br />\n<br />\n運動佔3成，飲食佔7成，戒哂油鹽糖包你瘦得好快"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"死就死在我唔識游水... 咁多運動我只識跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都會係飲食著手啦<br />\n<br />\n會食多d生果同菜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0023a390d54028e11cad011526b7d45321a5271","tid":981314,"uid":15112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T07:19:17.000Z","msg":"3年由120磅肥到宜家186磅..<br />\n我都要減.."},{"pid":"3a6e6d053d806182fe40c471d11e89fca0c19ef1","tid":981314,"uid":194143,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:53:25.000Z","msg":"幾點食野係冇影響<br />\n你六點食一碗飯200卡<br />\n八點食碗飯都同樣係200卡<br />\n重點係要食得健康 控制份量 <br />\n當然臨訓前食太多對胃腸消化都唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n做左最基本走糖走油先啦<br />\n試下做運動 計下減左幾多卡<br />\n當你發覺跑一個鐘頂多減四五百卡 食包薯片又會抵銷左既時候 你就唔會想食零食"},{"pid":"3f3905da1fa35ed0a8ebe9a9cd0010e832e7d2f9","tid":981314,"uid":32615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"05c0d0307733a50fbe89c9fe49e76a1b2dd9014e","tid":981314,"uid":171743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9051b6ff751cba26596321eaedf32379e25ad35","tid":981314,"uid":170934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"跑步對肥人膝頭太大負擔，可以去游水，同時間係飲食入手<br />\n<br />\n運動佔3成，飲食佔7成，戒哂油鹽糖包你瘦得好快"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"死就死在我唔識游水... 咁多運動我只識跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都會係飲食著手啦<br />\n<br />\n會食多d生果同菜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:29:03.000Z","msg":"康文署橢圓機<br />\n每日一個鐘  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n減多十磅再試下跑"},{"pid":"961addf6fba8a814d9ad612bef87e97a4d041793","tid":981314,"uid":84581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"跑空中單車<br />\n訓係到 雙腳凌空踩單車"},{"pid":"bd2248d833cc1dd654e44feb1d18e8ec32636cc7","tid":981314,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T11:33:57.000Z","msg":"跟youtube跳fitness dance"},{"pid":"fecfddfb1e09b603b8fb0e896d82d66268d7c44f","tid":981314,"uid":200286,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T13:19:10.000Z","msg":"我以前好唔健康咁由就黎70kg用左兩個月減到48kg。。。<br />\n廢都要講句 堅持真係好重要 <br />\n減肥好似儲蓄咁 儲一兩日錢就唔儲=白費<br />\n如果無運動底又體型大o既我唔建議一開始就跑步<br />\n好撚傷膝頭 到時傷左就俾左機會自己唔做運動=打回原型<br />\n你可以試下快走/行山/游水 相對對身體負荷無咁大<br />\n同埋飲食都好重要 其實靜係戒糖都好大效果 keep住戒皮膚都會變好<br />\n少食零食多食蔬果"},{"pid":"1ddc89f2486a22525e38b65ee8b1a7133f56ff78","tid":981314,"uid":169980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T13:25:13.000Z","msg":"上得呢度問減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就已經證明你減唔到<br />\n就算做都三分鐘熱度，以前太多呢D post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6816116d0ffa96d7161451ac1430a1a53f2c77b","tid":981314,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c0d0307733a50fbe89c9fe49e76a1b2dd9014e","tid":981314,"uid":171743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9051b6ff751cba26596321eaedf32379e25ad35","tid":981314,"uid":170934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"